    <p>SMART­PHONE</p>
    <p>$1,099, avail­able from Satur­day</p>
    <p>This An­droid smart­phone has a fea­ture not seen in many other smart­phones. Its 48-megapixel (MP) main rear cam­era has a gim­bal sys­tem to re­duce cam­era shake, thereby al­low­ing you to take clear photos and videos when in mo­tion.</p>
    <p>Its quad rear cam­era sys­tem also in­cludes an 8MP ul­tra-wide-an­gle cam­era, an 8MP tele­photo cam­era and a 13MP por­trait cam­era. A 32MP front-fac­ing cam­era lets you take high-res­o­lu­tion self­ies. Pow­ered by the Qual­comm Snap­dragon 765G pro­ces­sor, the X50 Pro 5G of­fers smooth mul­ti­task­ing, while its 6.56-inch dis­play has a high re­fresh rate of 90Hz.</p>

